1. Google Search
Google uses Machine Learning to understand my search query and rank the most relevant websites based on previous user data and behavior patterns.
2. YouTube Recommendations
ML analyzes my watch history, likes, and time spent on videos to suggest similar content I may be interested in.
3. Instagram Feed & Reels
AI tracks posts I like, share, or watch longer and uses ML models to show similar content on my feed.
4. Google Maps
Machine Learning predicts traffic conditions using real-time user location data and past traffic patterns.
5. Gmail Spam Filter
ML models analyze email content, sender details, and patterns to automatically detect and filter spam emails.
6. Voice Assistant (Google Assistant)
Speech recognition models convert my voice into text, and ML helps understand and respond to my commands.
7. Online Shopping (Amazon/Flipkart)
AI recommends products based on my previous searches, purchases, and browsing behavior.
8. Netflix Recommendations
ML studies my viewing history and ratings to suggest movies and shows I might like.
9. Mobile Face Unlock
AI uses image recognition and deep learning to identify my facial features and unlock the phone securely.
10. Keyboard Autocorrect & Suggestions
ML predicts the next word I want to type based on my typing habits and commonly used phrases.
